122
00:09:25,740 --> 00:09:27,156
Dia hanya perlu istirahat
selama beberapa hari.

123
00:09:27,880 --> 00:09:28,986
Bagaimana dengan Tae Pyung?

124
00:09:29,211 --> 00:09:30,986
Dia belum sadar.

125
00:09:31,750 --> 00:09:32,855
Dimana?

